2j\">{{cite web |url=https://www.whitehousehistory.org/african-americans-in-the-white-house-timeline|title=African Americans in the White House Timeline|accessdate=March 21, 2016|publisher= White House Historical Association}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"zQgqd\">{{Cite news|url=http://articles.sun-sentinel.com/1986-11-09/features/8603090262_1_white-house-brac-stone|title=Yugoslavs Claim Bit Of White House|last=Zentz|first=Wendy|date=November 9, 1986|work=SunSentinel|access-date=February 13, 2018|archive-url=|archive-date=|url-status=|language=en}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"L0Ydi\">{{Cite news|url=http://www.news-herald.com/article/HR/20101017/NEWS/310179993|title=Stone from island off Croatia made White House and ancient Roman palace|last=Podolak|first=Janet|date=October 17, 2010|work=The News-Herald|access-date=February 13, 2018|archive-url=|archive-date=|url-status=|language=en}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"J1ZuL\">{{Cite web|url=https://www.litosonline.com/en/articles/en/60/croatia-s-stone-industry-expanding|title=Croatia's Stone industry is expanding|last=|first=|date=|website=www.litosonline.com|language=en|archive-url=|archive-date=|url-status=|access-date=February 13, 2018}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"XEjY4\">{{cite web |url=http://www.whitehousemuseum.org/overview.htm|title=Overview of the White House|accessdate=November 9, 2007 |publisher= White House Museum}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"xVvhI\">{{cite book |author=Seale, William |title=The President's House, A History. Volume I. |year=1986 |publisher=White House Historical Association |pages=1, 23 |isbn=978-0-912308-28-9}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"8Rmlj\">{{cite book |author=Seale, William |title=The White House, The History of an American Idea |year=1992 |publisher=The American Institute of Architects Press |pages=35. 1 |isbn=978-1-55835-049-6}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"A3bMb\">{{cite book | last = Unger | first = Harlow | title = The Last Founding Father:James Monroe and a Nation's Call to Greatness | publisher = Da Capo Press | location = New