-story-of-the-white-houses-famous-magnolia-tree/2017/12/27/d81645a4-eb39-11e7-b698-91d4e35920a3_story.html |title=The story of the White House's famous magnolia tree |work=Washington Post |date=December 27, 2017 |accessdate=December 28, 2017}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"U4C8Y\">{{cite web|url=https://www.usnews.com/blogs/washington-whispers/2009/03/28/michelle-obama-goes-organic-and-brings-in-the-bees.html |title=Michelle Obama Goes Organic and Brings in the Bees |work=Washington Whispers |date=March 28, 2009 |accessdate=August 15, 2010}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"bXgDO\">{{cite web|last1=Freeze|first1=Christopher|title=The Time a Stolen Helicopter Landed on the White House Lawn - Robert Preston's wild ride.|url=http://www.airspacemag.com/history-of-flight/prestons-wild-white-house-ride-180962400/|website=Air & Space|publisher=Smithsonian|accessdate=March 22, 2017}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"JO4kZ\">{{cite news| url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/low/americas/1159300.stm |work=BBC News | title=White House security scares | date=February 7, 2001}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"ZScbt\">{{cite news|last= Johns |first= Joe |last2=Arena |first2=Kelli |last3=Koch|first3=Kathleen|title=Intruding pilots released without charges|url=http://www.cnn.com/2005/US/05/11/evacuation/index.html|publisher=CNN|date= May 12, 2005|accessdate=November 8, 2007}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"VuiCP\">{{cite web|title=Public Report of the White House Security Review|url=https://fas.org/irp/agency/ustreas/usss/t1pubrpt.html|publisher=Order of the Secretary of the Treasury|accessdate=November 8, 2007}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"F17OZ\">{{cite web|title=Statement of Committee of 100 on the Federal City and The National Coalition to Save Our Mall|url=http://www.savethemall.org/other/pa_ave.html|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20030425145712/http://www.savethemall.org/other/pa_ave.html|url-status=dead|archive-date=April 25, 2003|publisher=National Coalition to Save Our Mall, Inc|accessdate=November 8, 2007|year=2004}}</ref>\n\n<ref 